media-chromecast-slideshow - Chromecast Media Slideshow

USAGE:
    media-chromecast-slideshow <media-directory>

DESCRIPTION:
    Cast media files from directory to Chromecast as slideshow.

ARGUMENTS:
    media-directory
        Directory containing media files (required)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-media-share-chromecast-name NAME
        Chromecast device name

EXAMPLES:
    media-chromecast-slideshow /path/to/photos
    media-chromecast-slideshow ~/Pictures
